{"tid":2377950,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「價值型投資大師」預言美股大泡沫數月內將破滅","createTime":"2021-01-24T05:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T11:01:48.000Z","uid":288849,"like":110,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"1749e36f68c403127c6f8f419416046330d3c049","tid":2377950,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"「價值型投資大師」之稱的資產管理機構GMO創辦人葛拉漢（Jeremy Grantham預言美股大泡沫數月內將破滅？<br />\n「價值型投資大師」之稱的資產管理機構GMO創辦人葛拉漢（Jeremy Grantham）近日警告，美國股市原已處於「史詩級泡沫」之中，拜登的經濟復甦計劃，將推動泡沫達到更加危險的新高度，隨後將發生無可避免的崩盤，慘烈程度恐等同1929年華爾街股災，或是與2000年網路泡沫破滅相媲美。 葛拉漢近日接受《彭博》專訪時警告：「資金湧入還會再持續數週，你還有幾週的時間，把你最後的、生怕踏空的籌碼投入這場遊戲中，隨後就是上演驚人的崩盤。在市場達到這種超熱情水平時，泡沫總是會在數月內破滅，而非數年內，無一例外。」<br />\n<br />\n葛拉漢警告：慘烈程度恐如1929年股災<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3420536?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420536%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tah9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=4a012fc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420536%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&h=9e770f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3420536?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP</a>"},{"pid":"f802871bb87f214bbc1f7351765658d157c6aac1","tid":2377950,"uid":230146,"like":177,"dislike":4,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"淡友慘過做雞"},{"pid":"56cb986db9842a5862d5c8da02947084a4eed181","tid":2377950,"uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f802871bb87f214bbc1f7351765658d157c6aac1","tid":2377950,"uid":230146,"like":177,"dislike":4,"score":173,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:11:12.000Z","msg":"淡友慘過做雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" cla