的概率）在一至兩年後達到 2250 點，然後泡沫破裂&rdquo;，時間將是 2016 年總統大選時或大選結束後。"},{"pid":"1ca8b5deb81131da3332cebf0223a7dd3a4ac1a2","tid":2377950,"uid":129724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1749e36f68c403127c6f8f419416046330d3c049","tid":2377950,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:10:01.000Z","msg":"「價值型投資大師」之稱的資產管理機構GMO創辦人葛拉漢（Jeremy Grantham預言美股大泡沫數月內將破滅？<br />\n「價值型投資大師」之稱的資產管理機構GMO創辦人葛拉漢（Jeremy Grantham）近日警告，美國股市原已處於「史詩級泡沫」之中，拜登的經濟復甦計劃，將推動泡沫達到更加危險的新高度，隨後將發生無可避免的崩盤，慘烈程度恐等同1929年華爾街股災，或是與2000年網路泡沫破滅相媲美。 葛拉漢近日接受《彭博》專訪時警告：「資金湧入還會再持續數週，你還有幾週的時間，把你最後的、生怕踏空的籌碼投入這場遊戲中，隨後就是上演驚人的崩盤。在市場達到這種超熱情水平時，泡沫總是會在數月內破滅，而非數年內，無一例外。」<br />\n<br />\n葛拉漢警告：慘烈程度恐如1929年股災<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3420536?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420536%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tah9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=4a012fc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420536%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&h=9e770f72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3420536?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"咁你all in short 囉"},{"pid":"847f32f6b6bb276ab0f6b77faa8c911cd1d3fd03","tid":2377950,"uid":181502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"係人都知道係泡沫 到時只不過鬥走得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c7a96e7dcfb736c8afb4c09c2374ff7b55384a","tid":2377950,"uid":68728,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"美股個個都賺緊幾倍至十幾倍 <br />\n就算跌一半 大把人都仲係贏緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal